descript.abstract: This data set is known as Cadastre Real Estate Parcel Tracts and contains the tract map boundaries for the Bakersfield general plan area for Bakersfield, CA.
descript.purpose: The data set was created to aid in local GIS and mapping applications and to allow the visualizations of city growth over the years.
descript.supplinf: Derived from COGO'd tract maps provided by the Bakersfield Planning Department.
